{"tid":1533413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"好撚攰呀，依加仲未有Twitter個啲我屌你老母，手足打生打死，你禁幾個制都唔肯？","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:12:01.000Z","uid":63045,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5992f244a6d435a400397fb3e54fb0c3bdbf7f75","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先開個新gmail,然後用個gmail同我開個twitter, 唔好用個人資料，廢時比人秋後算帳。網頁版gmail唔洗電話都申請到。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n日日叫人放上Twitter,又唔撚幫手retweet,條tweet自己曉飛啊？見到民記得個幾千個follow仲有攬炒巴個啲得萬幾，連登啲人去晒邊？文宣戰線嚴重缺人，twitter手足們需要大家支援，一齊推爆#ChiNazi<br />\n大家一人一日retweet with comment 幾下，幫手分擔下，真係好攰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開完ac慢慢follow人，太快會叫你綁電話號碼，可以search #followbackhongkong,follow 番啲手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咩最後一戰呀？明明就係無限之戰，你對手係赤納粹，有二三十年要捱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nSorry,但唔屌唔成器，身邊十個有九個都未有twitter真係嬲嬲地，明明都係後生仔，咁快接受唔到新事物？<br />\n停止連登圍爐，係到打hashtag 係唔會有人睇到咖....幫幫手做實事"},{"pid":"a794bf363ff34e1498857bb6eeff69b51fed2add","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3d1fcda9dd17199b616a6619d980ed927638a24","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"801cad1b69f82141ff34453d9ad8e2e01715b8b8","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"申請咗ac未呀"},{"pid":"576a4e39024e444ae7dd09218386dace1718607a","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"申請咗ac未呀"},{"pid":"2009d5e1809c47eaace076ab2318c4dfeb4506c0","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母無人理"},{"pid":"597d114769bc7cf7be3b2ef7ebd78c740f458e3b","tid":1533413,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"一早申咗"},{"pid":"03c84c3846961900cdbacd91da98db8bb9209847","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"拰"},{"pid":"571759a585c9634ef5f72151909fe7bc590c31ae","tid":1533413,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5c5baf16bb7d91442600e1564047f1cecec91f","tid":1533413,"uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d30265f14756b75a91dcc071155bd3261f8ed0d","tid":1533413,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"文宣組係文，我地係宣<br />\n有文無宣食得屎"},{"pid":"8d41730fbc8cdb1ecb2b897806f842228893a4d8","tid":1533413,"uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"你地仲用fuckbook? 連用twitter既決心都無仲學人講抵制<br />\n無人叫你地要即刻放棄fuckbook/ig，仍然可以做文宣，但同樣地可以係其他方面減少用<br />\n再用埋twitter比壓力垃圾朱西伯格個奶共下屬<br />\nfuckbook都要做生意，會計住用家online既時間同廣告既reach&amp;click rate，佢見少左自然有壓力，交唔到朱西伯格會問責<br />\n呢個亦係最有用既方法令fuckbook主動block 5毛"},{"pid":"9eb65f239fc4d340451ee8aa99be42835062bb93","tid":1533413,"uid":280326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco